<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="101" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="8.[168,775,1541,1837]" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[168,286,1541,1565]" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Ground-color light brown, with areas of gray pruinosity. Legs light brown. Dorsocentral setae 2+3. Prealar seta strong, longer than anterior notopleural seta. Katepisternal setae 2+2. Vein 
<emphasis box="[615,683,1643,1667]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">dm-cu</emphasis>
slightly curved. Vein 
<emphasis box="[316,412,1677,1700]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
A 
<subScript attach="left" box="[331,338,1684,1698]" fontSize="6" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">1</subScript>
+CuA 
<subScript attach="left" box="[404,412,1684,1698]" fontSize="6" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">2</subScript>
</emphasis>
reaching the wing margin. Wing with spots on vein 
<emphasis box="[365,391,1712,1735]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
R 
<subScript attach="left" box="[383,391,1718,1732]" fontSize="6" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">1</subScript>
</emphasis>
apex and reaching the vein 
<emphasis box="[685,711,1711,1734]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">Sc</emphasis>
apex, between vein 
<emphasis box="[315,357,1746,1769]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
R 
<subScript attach="none" box="[332,357,1752,1766]" fontSize="6" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">4+5</subScript>
</emphasis>
and vein 
<emphasis box="[455,477,1746,1769]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">M</emphasis>
base, vein 
<emphasis box="[595,634,1746,1769]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">r-m</emphasis>
, vein 
<emphasis box="[699,767,1745,1769]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">dm-cu</emphasis>
, 2 on vein 
<emphasis box="[281,349,1779,1803]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">dm-cu</emphasis>
corners and an inconspicuous spot on vein 
<emphasis box="[221,263,1814,1837]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
R 
<subScript attach="left" box="[238,263,1820,1834]" fontSize="6" pageId="8" pageNumber="101">2+3</subScript>
</emphasis>
apex.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
